doctor.name: Dr. Tahmina Begum Poly
doctor.workplace: North East Medical College & Hospital, Sylhet
doctor.info: Dr. Tahmina Begum Poly is a Gynecologist in Sylhet. Her qualification is MBBS, FCPS (Gynae & Obst). She is a Assistant Professor (Gyne & Obs Dept) at North East Medical College & Hospital, Sylhet. She regularly provides treatment to her patients at Mount Adora Hospital, Nayasarak, Sylhet. Practicing hour of Dr. Tahmina Begum Poly at Mount Adora Hospital, Nayasarak, Sylhet is 6pm to 8.30pm (Closed: Friday).
